                <zone fixed-size='72' forceUpdate='true' h='8889' id='55' type-v2='text' w='86937' x='500' y='85000'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Key Insights</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• NYC Taxi generated over $2.5B revenue from 106M+ trips, showing strong transportation demand across the city.</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Credit card payments generated nearly 5× more revenue than cash, indicating dominant digital payment behavior.</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>• Revenue and trip demand consistently increased from 2021–2023, while Thursday contributed the highest weekly revenue.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
